 Hendrina police spokesperson, David Mbenekazi, said that they suspect heavy mist was the cause of the accident wherein a truck drove over a car. All the occupants of the car, believed to be on their way to work, perished in the accident. The wreck was in such a state that it is unclear what the make and model of the vehicle was.
